Learn More About Savvion Components <http://www.savvion.info/mailings/february2002/feb06/links/componentslink.htm>According to Gartner Group, by 2003, at least 70 percent of all new applications will be built primarily from components. Components offer extensive time and cost savings by letting developers integrate multiple software modules when creating new applications, reducing in-house programming effort, leveraging new Web Services, and increasing software quality.

