In direct response to market demand for components, Savvion offers IT managers and software developers powerful components for quickly developing e-business applications at a fraction of the price and time they spend today.

Learn More About Savvion Components <http://www.savvion.info/mailings/february2002/feb06/links/componentslink.htm>

Engineered to boost productivity and speed time to market, Savvion Enterprise JavaBeans BizComponents allow developers to: 

Easily add high-level services to a broad range of applications

Speed the development and deployment of applications via intuitive graphical user interfaces

Support highly scalable, reliable services in distributed environments with J2EE compliance

